<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Game Theory on QiView</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/</link><description>Recent content in Game Theory on QiView</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>博弈论与机制设计教程入口（曹乾2016）</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/game-theory-tutorial-entry/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/game-theory-tutorial-entry/</guid><description>整合版网页教程入口：进入《博弈论与机制设计（曹乾译，2016）》章节目录与全书内容。</description></item><item><title>不完全信息博弈：贝叶斯纳什均衡与类型空间</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/incomplete-information-bayesian-games/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/incomplete-information-bayesian-games/</guid><description>建立不完全信息博弈的Harsanyi类型空间框架，推导贝叶斯纳什均衡的分析方法，通过双边拍卖、信贷配给和贸易谈判等应用案例说明私有信息对均衡结果的深刻影响。</description></item><item><title>信号博弈：劳动力市场模型、精炼贝叶斯均衡与均衡选择</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/signaling-games-spence-model/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/signaling-games-spence-model/</guid><description>系统建立信号博弈的分析框架与精炼贝叶斯均衡概念，深入推导Spence劳动力市场信号模型的分离均衡与混同均衡，讨论均衡精炼标准与信号传递的本质逻辑。</description></item><item><title>动态博弈与子博弈精炼：序贯理性与承诺问题</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/dynamic-games-subgame-perfect/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/dynamic-games-subgame-perfect/</guid><description>系统建立扩展式博弈的分析框架，详解逆向归纳法与子博弈精炼纳什均衡的概念，通过最后通牒、入场威慑、连锁店悖论等案例阐明序贯理性与不可置信威胁的核心问题。</description></item><item><title>完全信息静态博弈：纳什均衡的存在、计算与精炼</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/static-games-nash-equilibrium/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/static-games-nash-equilibrium/</guid><description>系统阐述完全信息静态博弈的形式化框架，涵盖优势策略消除、纳什均衡的存在性定理、纯策略与混合策略均衡的计算，以及理性化等精炼概念。</description></item><item><title>寡头市场中的静态博弈：古诺、伯特兰与斯坦伯格模型</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/oligopoly-games-applications/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/oligopoly-games-applications/</guid><description>以工业组织为背景，系统推导古诺数量竞争、伯特兰价格竞争与斯坦伯格领导者模型的均衡结果，对比在位者-进入者博弈中的承诺与威慑策略。</description></item><item><title>机制设计：显示原理、激励相容与拍卖理论</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/mechanism-design-auctions/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/mechanism-design-auctions/</guid><description>介绍机制设计的核心框架：社会选择函数、显示原理、激励相容与个人理性约束，推导最优拍卖设计（Myerson最优机制），以及收入等价定理的证明与直觉。</description></item><item><title>重复博弈、合作均衡与Folk定理</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/repeated-games-folk-theorem/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/repeated-games-folk-theorem/</guid><description>分析有限与无限重复博弈的均衡结构，建立无限重复博弈Folk定理的严格形式，讨论触发策略、冷酷策略、以及合作如何通过未来惩罚承诺实现。</description></item><item><title>博弈论基础入门教程</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/game-theory-basics/</link><pubDate>Fri, 05 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/game-theory-basics/</guid><description>博弈论基本概念、常见模型与应用场景的入门指南</description></item></channel></rss>